1591a7"},"outputs":[{"output_type":"stream","name":"stderr","text":["/usr/local/lib/python3.12/dist-packages/langgraph/checkpoint/serde/encrypted.py:5: LangChainPendingDeprecationWarning: The default value of `allowed_objects` will change in a future version. Pass an explicit value (e.g., allowed_objects='messages' or allowed_objects='core') to suppress this warning.\n","  from langgraph.checkpoint.serde.jsonplus import JsonPlusSerializer\n"]},{"output_type":"stream","name":"stdout","text":["✅ Agent created with structured output\n"]}],"source":["from langchain.agents import create_agent\n","from langchain.tools import tool\n","from pydantic import BaseModel, Field\n","from typing import Literal\n","\n","\n","# Define the structured output\n","class SignupEmailOutput(BaseModel):\n","    to: str = Field(description=\"Email address\")\n","    icp_fit: Literal[\"high\", \"medium\", \"low\", \"unknown\"] = Field(description=\"ICP fit classification\")\n","    reason: str = Field(description=\"Brief reasoning for classification\")\n","    subject: str = Field(description=\"Email subject line\")\n","    body: str = Field(description=\"Email body text\")\n","\n","\n","# Text between the two \"\"\"s is our prompt (FEEL FREE TO CHANGE)\n","SYSTEM_PROMPT = \"\"\"\n","Process this signup to your dev tool SaaS called 'Glop'.\n","Return icp_fit, reason, and a short personalized welcome email.\n","Welcome email should mention user's current role and company.\n","Make sure the email is concise, conversationally informal, and professional.\n","\"\"\"\n","\n","# Create the agent\n","agent = create_agent(\n","    \"openai:gpt-4o-mini\",\n","    tools=[],  # No tools needed — this is a reasoning-only agent\n","    system_prompt=SYSTEM_PROMPT,\n","    response_format=SignupEmailOutput,\n",")\n","\n","print(\"✅ Agent created with structured output\")"]},{"cell_type":"markdown","id":"fc51d87d","metadata":{"id":"fc51d87d"},"source":["### Test the agent with a single record"]},{"cell_type":"code","execution_count":null,"id":"c24c1aba","metadata":{"colab":{"base_uri":"https://localhost:8080/"},"id":"c24c1aba","executionInfo":{"status":"ok","timestamp":1778787456763,"user_tz":420,"elapsed":3483,"user":{"displayName":"Vijay Misra","userId":"00234019357047153423"}},"outputId":"ef2a9bfa-5937-4f7b-f116-4eddcc9427a0"},"outputs":[{"output_type":"stream","name":"stdout","text":["ICP Fit:  high\n","Reason:   Sarah's role as VP of Engineering in a SaaS company of 500 employees indicates a strong alignment with our target audience for Glop.\n","Subject:  Welcome to Glop, Sarah!\n","Body:  Hey Sarah,\n","\n","Welcome to Glop! We're thrilled to have you on board as the VP of Engineering at Acme Corp. We believe our tools can make a significant impact in your workflow. \n","\n","If you have any questions or need assistance, just hit reply!\n","\n","Cheers,\n","The Glop Team\n"]}],"source":["result = agent.invoke({\n","    \"messages\": [{\n","        \"role\": \"user\",\n","        \"content\": \"\"\"Process this signup:\n","email: sarah@acmecorp.com\n","first_name: Sarah\n","company_name: Acme Corp\n","role: VP of Engineering\n","industry: SaaS\n","company_size: 500\"\"\"\n","    }]\n","})\n","\n","# Extract structured response\n","output = result[\"structured_response\"]\n","print(f\"ICP Fit:  {output.icp_fit}\")\n","print(f\"Reason:   {output.reason}\")\n","print(f\"Subject:  {output.subject}\")\n","print(f\"Body:  {output.body}\")"]},{"cell_type":"markdown","id":"2aa486cb","metadata":{"id":"2aa486cb"},"source":["### Verify Traces in LangSmith\n","\n","Open [smith.langchain.com](https://smith.langchain.com) → **default** project.\n","\n","You should see:\n","- ✅ A trace for the single invocation above\n","- ✅ Full input/output captured\n","- ✅ Latency, token usage, and model info\n"]},{"cell_type":"markdown","id":"352118e5","metadata":{"id":"352118e5"},"source":["---\n","## Step 2: Offline Evaluation with DeepEval\n","\n","\n"]},{"cell_type":"markdown","id":"a22f0b1c","metadata":{"id":"a22f0b1c"},"source":["### Upload golden dataset to LangSmith (manually)\n","\n","Before we start running the agent, we need a golden dataset in LangSmith. This is the ground truth we'll evaluate against later.\n","\n","**Do this now in the LangSmith UI:**\n","\n","0. Download the [golden_dataset.jsonl](https://drive.google.com/file/d/1PPpfHP5BIYGwReZ_8S7dK60vWWrAVrxb/view?usp=sharing) file\n","1. Go to [smith.langchain.com](https://smith.langchain.com)\n","2. Click **Datasets & Experiments** in the left sidebar\n","3. Click **+ Dataset**\n","4. Click **Click to upload**\n","5. Name it `golden-dataset`\n","6. Upload the [golden_dataset.jsonl](https://drive.google.com/file/d/1PPpfHP5BIYGwReZ_8S7dK60vWWrAVrxb/view?usp=sharing) file\n","7. Verify"]},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":["### Fetch golden dataset locally"],"metadata":{"id":"yinZn-XtUZ3A"},"id":"yinZn-XtUZ3A"},{"cell_type":"code","source":["from langsmith import Client\n","\n","ls = Client()\n","\n","dataset_name = \"golden-dataset\"\n","examples = list(ls.list_examples(dataset_name=dataset_name))\n","\n","print(f\"Loaded {len(examples)} examples\")\n","print(\"Sample inputs keys:\", examples[0].inputs.keys())\n","print(\"Sample outputs keys:\", examples[0].outputs.keys())"],"metadata":{"colab":{"base_uri":"https://localhost:8080/"},"id":"5-MWR3h-_yEc","executionInfo":{"status":"ok","timestamp":1778787457497,"user_tz":420,"elapsed":731,"user":{"displayName":"Vijay Misra","userId":"00234019357047153423"}},"outputId":"c89b04b2-8cfa-4872-b44b-6c8a58b82923"},"id":"5-MWR3h-_yEc","execution_count":null,"outputs":[{"output_type":"stream","name":"stdout","text":["Loaded 6 examples\n","Sample inputs keys: dict_keys(['messages'])\n","Sample outputs keys: dict_keys(['outputs_1'])\n"]}]},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":["### Create evaluators with DeepEval"],"metadata":{"id":"4fy2YSlWUeJH"},"id":"4fy2YSlWUeJH"},{"cell_type":"code","source":["from deepeval.metrics import JsonCorrectnessMetric, ExactMatchMetric, GEval\n","from deepeval.test_case import LLMTestCase, LLMTestCaseParams\n","\n","# Exact match metric\n","icp_fit_evaluator = ExactMatchMetric(\n","    threshold=1.0,\n",")\n","\n","# LLM-as-a-judge\n","email_evaluator = GEval(\n","    name=\"Email Quality\",\n","    criteria=\"Evaluate if the email is professional, personalized (uses the person's name/role/company), concise (under 150 words), and does not hallucinate facts not present in the input.\",\n","    evaluation_params=[LLMTestCaseParams.INPUT, LLMTestCaseParams.ACTUAL_OUTPUT],\n","    model=\"gpt-4o-mini\",\n","    threshold=0.5\n",")\n","\n","icp_fit_evaluator.include_reason = True\n","email_evaluator.include_reason = True"],"metadata":{"id":"o2v5-XrcANaa","colab":{"base_uri":"https://localhost:8080/"},"executionInfo":{"status":"ok","timestamp":1778789768017,"user_tz":420,"elapsed":67,"user":{"displayName":"Vijay Misra","userId":"00234019357047153423"}},"outputId":"7381ae70-cccc-427b-da21-1aab76aed4ae"},"id":"o2v5-XrcANaa","execution_count":null,"outputs":[{"output_type":"stream","name":"stderr","text":["/tmp/ipykernel_15771/425009796.py:2: DeprecationWarning: 'LLMTestCaseParams' is deprecated and will be removed in a future release. Use 'SingleTurnParams' instead.\n","  from deepeval.test_case import LLMTestCase, LLMTestCaseParams\n"]}]},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":["### Run evals across all golden dataset"],"metadata":{"id":"cSA66vg1Ukuz"},"id":"cSA66vg1Ukuz"},{"cell_type":"code","execution_count":null,"id":"407e066e","metadata":{"id":"407e066e","colab":{"base_uri":"https://localhost:8080/","height":198,"referenced_widgets":["63e39aba11d44bce90165eb2151cfd8f","3a53f16d836741d4a2860265d54719d8","09048316faf44135b87ada12eb61144b","cc21fa1b92df438c83a0443cdd7fb73a","9200b3c23f2a44108bdaace0cc8330e2","0cfae74f9f824f41a5c7b1686e6e9c65","9f9f519a0ba042649eb1b258c3563fe8","a5c947dd5e914716973235d1f1ce5d78","aa3713776e454921864ae7082324ccad","06eae2051ee74394b1dde0d700a61272","0af93f6c3f2c4